Navigate to other release versions of Doxee Platform Business Designer

[6.6](https://docs.doxee.com/docs/en/business-designer-6-6)

[6.7](https://docs.doxee.com/docs/en/business-designer-6-7)

You can activate and deactivate the spell check function in the title bar by clicking the ABC- icon.

![](data:image/png;base64,)

After activation, the ABC icon is extended with a tick and all spelling errors in the text are underlined with a red wavy line.

With a right click on the highlighted word suggestions and the options *Add to dictionary*, *Ignore *and *Delete word *are displayed. If there is no suggestion from the dictionary, only the options *Add to dictionary*, *Ignore *and *Delete word *are displayed. By selecting a suggestion, the selected word is replaced and the wavy line disappears.

![](data:image/jpeg;base64,)

If a word has been added to the ignore list, it can be removed from the list with a right click and the selection *Remove from ignored*.

![](data:image/jpeg;base64,)

### Language Selection
Any number of dictionaries in different languages can be added to the Business Designer configuration. To the right of the ABC icon, the language of the dictionary can be selected by clicking on the arrow:

![](data:image/png;base64,)
